text: Alon Carl Wieland (April 26, 1935 â€“ January 22, 2022) was an American Republican politician and businessman. He was a member of the North Dakota House of Representatives, from 2002 to 2014. He was the Commissioner of Cass County, North Dakota from 1983 to 2003. Wieland was born in Underwood, North Dakota. Wieland died in West Fargo, North Dakota on January 22, 2022, at the age of 86.Former state legislator, Cass County commissioner dies at 86 ==References== Category:1935 births Category:2022 deaths Category:State legislators of the United States Category:Politicians from North Dakota Category:Businesspeople from North Dakota Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
